  {
      "account": "NdUL5oDPD159KeFpD5A9zw5xNF1xLX6nLT",
      "scopes": "WitnessRules",
      "rules": [{
              "action": "Allow",
              "condition": {
                  "type": "Boolean",
                  "expression": true
              }
          }
      ]
  }
  ```

- Not: Logical NOT. It reverses other conditions.

  “expression”=<Condition>

  ```
